sentences: He left the band in 1984 and later worked as a songwriter.
He released a solo album, American Street, in 1999.
George McCorkle pursued music as a career after having been drafted into the Navy and serving from 1967 to 1968.
McCorkle was diagnosed with cancer in early June 2007 and died soon afterward, in Lebanon, Tennessee.
